                      <p dir="RTL" style="margin:0cm 36pt 8pt 0cm;text-align:right;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:embed"><span style="font-family:Symbol"><span>·<span style="font:7pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span dir="RTL"></span><span lang="HE">תשלום זה לא
